﻿@model WebApp.Models.TmOrderException
<!-- 弹出窗体form表单 -->
<div id="exdetailswindow" hidden="hidden" class="easyui-window"
     title="登记异常"
     data-options="modal:true,
                    closed:true,
                    maximized:false,
                    iconCls:'icon-more',
                    footer:'#windowfooter',
                    closeDuration:200,
                    closeAnimation:'slide',
                    openDuration:300,
                    openAnimation:'slide',
                    onOpen:function(){
                       $(this).window('vcenter');
                       $(this).window('hcenter');
                    },
                    onRestore:function(){
                    },
                    onMaximize:function(){
                    }
                    " style="width:1350px;height:520px">
  <!-- begin toolbar -->
  <div class="window-body-toolbar">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-8">
        <div class="btn-group btn-group-sm">
          <button onclick="addtmorderexception()" class="btn btn-default">
            <i class="fa fa-floppy-o"></i> @Html.L("Save")
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-group btn-group-sm" style="display:none">
          <button onclick="todo()" class="btn btn-default">
            <i class="fa fa-print"></i> ToDo
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4 text-align-right">
        <div class="btn-group btn-group-sm">
          <button type="button" class="btn   btn-success" onclick="closeexwindow()">
            <i class="fa fa-chevron-left"></i>
            @Html.L("Close")
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- end toolbar -->
  <!-- begin window body -->
  <div class="widget-body">
    <form id="tmorderexception_form"
          class="easyui-form form-horizontal padding-10"
          method="post"
          data-options="novalidate:true,
                            onChange: function(target){
                              hasChanged = true;
                             },
                             onLoadSuccess:function(data){
                               hasChanged = false;
                             }">
      @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
      <!--Primary Key-->
      <input type="hidden" id="@Html.IdFor(model => model.Id)"
             name="@Html.NameFor(model => model.Id)"
             value="@Html.ValueFor(model => model.Id)" />
      <fieldset>
        <div id="fmfieldset" class="form-group-sm">
          <!--end row-->
          <div class="row" style="margin:0px">


            <!--派车单号-->
            <div class="col-3 col-md-3 has-feedback" style="padding:0px;margin:0px">
              <label class="control-label" style="width:30%">@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.ShipOrderNo)</label>
              <input id="@Html.IdFor(model => model.ShipOrderNo)"
                     name="@Html.NameFor(model => model.ShipOrderNo)"
                     value="@Html.ValueFor(model => model.ShipOrderNo)"
                     tabindex="10"
                     class="easyui-textbox"
                     style="width:68%"
                     type="text"
                     data-options="prompt:'@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.ShipOrderNo)',
								 required:false,readonly:true,
                                 validType: 'length[8,20]'
                                 " />
            </div>
            <!--车辆-->
            <div class="col-3 col-md-3 has-feedback" style="padding:0px;margin:0px">
              <label class="control-label" style="width:30%">@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.VEHICLERES_ID)</label>
              <input id="@Html.IdFor(model => model.VEHICLERES_ID)"
                     name="@Html.NameFor(model => model.VEHICLERES_ID)"
                     value="@Html.ValueFor(model => model.VEHICLERES_ID)"
                     tabindex="11"
                     class="easyui-textbox"
                     style="width:68%"
                     type="text"
                     data-options="prompt:'@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.VEHICLERES_ID)',
								 required:false,readonly:true,
                                 validType: 'length[0,40]'
                                 " />
            </div>
            <!--车板号-->
            <div class="col-3 col-md-3 has-feedback" style="padding:0px;margin:0px">
              <label class="control-label" style="width:30%">@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.PLATENUMBER_P)</label>
              <input id="@Html.IdFor(model => model.PLATENUMBER_P)"
                     name="@Html.NameFor(model => model.PLATENUMBER_P)"
                     value="@Html.ValueFor(model => model.PLATENUMBER_P)"
                     tabindex="12"
                     class="easyui-textbox"
                     style="width:68%"
                     type="text"
                     data-options="prompt:'@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.PLATENUMBER_P)',
								 required:false,readonly:true,
                                 validType: 'length[0,20]'
                                 " />
            </div>
            <!--司机姓名-->
            <div class="col-3 col-md-3 has-feedback" style="padding:0px;margin:0px">
              <label class="control-label" style="width:30%">@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.ZSJXM)</label>
              <input id="@Html.IdFor(model => model.ZSJXM)"
                     name="@Html.NameFor(model => model.ZSJXM)"
                     value="@Html.ValueFor(model => model.ZSJXM)"
                     tabindex="13"
                     class="easyui-textbox"
                     style="width:68%"
                     type="text"
                     data-options="prompt:'@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.ZSJXM)',
								 required:false,readonly:true,
                                 validType: 'length[0,20]'
                                 " />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row" style="margin:0px">

            <!--调度员-->
            <div class="col-3 col-md-3 has-feedback" style="padding:0px;margin:0px">
              <label class="control-label" style="width:30%">@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.ZDDY)</label>
              <input id="@Html.IdFor(model => model.ZDDY)"
                     name="@Html.NameFor(model => model.ZDDY)"
                     value="@Html.ValueFor(model => model.ZDDY)"
                     tabindex="14"
                     class="easyui-textbox"
                     style="width:68%"
                     type="text"
                     data-options="prompt:'@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.ZDDY)',
								 required:false,readonly:true,
                                 validType: 'length[0,10]'
                                 " />
            </div>
            <!--派车日期-->
            <div class="col-3 col-md-3 has-feedback" style="padding:0px;margin:0px">
              <label class="control-label" style="width:30%">@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.ZPCRQ)</label>
              <input id="@Html.IdFor(model => model.ZPCRQ)"
                     name="@Html.NameFor(model => model.ZPCRQ)"
                     value="@Html.ValueFor(model => model.ZPCRQ)"
                     tabindex="15"
                     class="easyui-datebox"
                     style="width:68%"
                     type="text"
                     data-options="prompt:'@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.ZPCRQ)',
								 required:false,readonly:true,
								 formatter:dateformatter" />
            </div>
            <!--备注-->
            <div class="col-3 col-md-3 has-feedback" style="padding:0px;margin:0px">
              <label class="control-label" style="width:30%">@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.ZCOMMENT)</label>
              <input id="@Html.IdFor(model => model.ZCOMMENT)"
                     name="@Html.NameFor(model => model.ZCOMMENT)"
                     value="@Html.ValueFor(model => model.ZCOMMENT)"
                     tabindex="16"
                     class="easyui-textbox"
                     style="width:68%"
                     type="text"
                     data-options="prompt:'@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.ZCOMMENT)',
								 required:false,readonly:true,
                                 validType: 'length[0,256]'
                                 " />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <div class="row" style="padding-top:10px">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <table id="extb" class="table table-bordered">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <td width="80px">方向</td>
                  <td width="100px">集装箱号</td>
                  <td width="100px">FWO号</td>
                  <td width="100px">业务类型</td>
                  <td width="130px" >异常类型</td>
                  <td width="130px" >异常分类</td>
                  <td>异常说明</td>
                </tr>
                </thead>
              <tbody>
                
              </tbody>
              </table>
          </div>
        </div>
        </fieldset>
    </form>

    <!--end form表单界面-->
    <!--========================================================================================-->
  </div>
  <!--end window body -->
</div>
<div id="windowfooter" style="padding:5px;">&nbsp;</div>
<!-- 弹出窗体form表单 -->
<!-- 弹出编辑对话框 -->
<script>
  function closeexwindow() {
    $('#exdetailswindow').window('close');
  }
  function openexwindow(item) {
    $('#exdetailswindow').window('open');
    item.VEHICLERES_ID = item.ZCPH;
    item.PLATENUMBER_P = item.ZCBH;
    item.ZPCRQ = item.ZDDPCSJ;
    item.ZCOMMENT = item.ZBZ;
    $('#tmorderexception_form').form('load', item);

    var rows = $shippingtaskitemsdg.datagrid('getRows');
    $("#extb tbody").empty();
    rows.forEach(item => {
      var d = item.Drirect == "0" ? "去程" : "回程";
      var btype = '';
      switch (item.TRQ_TYPE) {
        case 'OE01':
          btype = '海运出口-整箱'
          break;
        case 'OE02':
          btype = '海运出口-散箱'
          break;
        case 'OI01':
          btype = '海运进口-整箱'
          break;
        case 'OI02':
          btype = '海运进口-散箱'
          break;
      }
      var s1 = $("<select id=\"ExType\" name=\"ExType\" />");
      for (var val in abtypedatasource) {
        $("<option />", { value: abtypedatasource[val].value, text: abtypedatasource[val].text  }).appendTo(s1);
      }
      var s2 = $("<select id=\"ExType\" name=\"ExType\" />");
      for (var val in abclassdatasource) {
        $("<option />", { value: abclassdatasource[val].value, text: abclassdatasource[val].text }).appendTo(s2);
      }
     
      var tr = `<tr><td> ${d} </td>
                    <td> ${item.TURES_ID}     </td>
                    <td> ${item.TRQ_ID}     </td>
                    <td> ${btype}     </td>
                    <td> <select    name="extype" >${s1.html()}</select> </td>
                    <td> <select    name="exclass" >${s2.html()}</select> </td>
                    <td> <input style="width:100%" type="text" name="description" value="" /> </td>
               </tr>`;
      $("#extb tbody").append(tr);
    });
    
   
  }
  function addtmorderexception() {
    if ($('#tmorderexception_form').form('enableValidation').form('validate')) {
      let tmorderexception = $('#tmorderexception_form').serializeJSON();
      let url = '/TmOrderExceptions/InsertItems';
      let data = [];
      $("#extb > tbody  > tr").each(function () {
        var TURES_ID = $(this).find("td:eq(1)").text().trim();
        var TRQ_ID = $(this).find("td:eq(2)").text().trim();
        var ExType = $(this).find("td:eq(4) select").val();
        var ExClass = $(this).find("td:eq(5) select").val();
        var ExDescription = $(this).find("td:eq(6) input").val();
        //console.log(TURES_ID, TRQ_ID, ExType, ExClass, ExDescription);
        data.push({ ShipOrderNo: tmorderexception.ShipOrderNo, TRQ_ID: TRQ_ID, TURES_ID: TURES_ID, ExType: ExType, ExClass: ExClass, ExDescription: ExDescription });
      })
      console.log(data);
      var token = $('input[name="__RequestVerificationToken"]', $('#tmorderexception_form')).val();
      $.ajax({
        type: "POST",
        url: url,
        data: {
          data: data
        },
        dataType: 'json',
        contentType: 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=utf-8'
      })
        .done(response => {
          if (response.success) {
            hasChanged = false;
            $('#tmorderexception_form').form('disableValidation');
            $dg.datagrid('reload');
            closeexwindow();
            toastr.success("保存成功");
          } else {
            $.messager.alert("错误", response.err, "error");
          }
        })
        .fail((jqXHR, textStatus, errorThrown) => {
          $.messager.alert('异常', `${jqXHR.status}: ${jqXHR.statusText} `, 'error');
        });
    }
  }

</script>